NYSE Euronext’s Liffe May Stay in London After Merger, FT Says

-- B y   B l a n c h e   G a t t
-- 
2011-02-14T03:03:25Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-14/nyse-euronext-s-liffe-may-stay-in-london-after-merger-ft-says.html
NYSE Euronext’s Liffe derivatives
market won’t be closed down or shifted to continental  Europe  as
a result of the planned merger of Deutsche Boerse AG and  NYSE
Euronext  and it is expected to remain intact and in  London , the
Financial Times reported, citing people familiar with the
matter.  To contact the reporter on this story:
